      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Ling Sync 0.1.1\n\n- Describe Ling search and AI-assisted recall in the plugin manifest.\n- Respect each Vault's configured settings directory when filtering paths.\n- Add searchable plugin settings for Obsidian 1.13 and newer while retaining compatibility with 1.11.4.\n- Reconcile after desktop or mobile foreground resume.\n- Remove stale Ling mirrors when a Markdown file exceeds the 2 MiB limit and restore them after the file returns under the limit.\n- Publish only `main.js` and `manifest.json`, with GitHub build provenance for `main.js`.\n",
